  "description": "A close-up photograph showcases a stem of vibrant purple Salvia flowers in varying stages of bloom. The blossoms are a soft lavender to deep violet hue, exhibiting a unique shape with a prominent lower lip and darker markings. Several flowers are fully open, revealing intricate internal structures, while others are still buds, tightly closed and showing hints of green. The stem is a muted green-brown, providing a contrasting backdrop to the vivid flowers. The background is a soft, out-of-focus yellow-green, creating a blurred bokeh effect. The image is well-lit, highlighting the textures and details of the flowers and stem.",
